Welcome. Would you like to stay at the Holy Light
Inn for 1500 Lo per night?

Thank you very much. Please feel free to use any
available room and take your time...
It seems like you don't have enough money...
Wow! A naked girl entered the room!

You can't go on a proper adventure outside with
monsters and bandits, and even in the dungeon
there are demons.

Wait, wait, you're in the wrong room! Take off
your clothes in your own room, okay?

Calling magical girls mere weapons used by
demons... Well, it's a bit harsh to say that, but
it's true that they can't resist them with any
other power.

It seems that there are many magical girls in this
world who find it too difficult and end up
dropping out. Well, it's not surprising, they have
to continue fighting those terrifying demons.
